{
    // ============================================================
    // JobHunter Launch Configurations
    // ============================================================
    // PIPELINE
    //   Full Pipeline              scrape -> tailor -> apply (daily cap enforced)
    //   Pipeline (Refresh Profile) same, but forces re-seed of answer bank from profile.yaml
    //
    // INDIVIDUAL STEPS
    //   Scrape Only                pull jobs from job boards into DB (status=new)
    //   Tailor Only                GPT-4o resume + cover letter for new jobs (status->tailored)
    //   Apply Only                 submit applications for all tailored jobs
    //   Seed Answer Bank           populate answer bank from profile.yaml (run before apply)
    //
    // SINGLE-JOB TESTING (debug loop)
    //   Apply Job (by ID)          apply to one specific job — prompts for ID
    //   Apply Job --debug          same, but pauses after DOM pre-fill + each vision round for inspection
    //   Apply Job (next available) apply to next tailored job — no prompt
    //   Retry Failed Jobs          reset failed -> tailored so Apply Job can re-run them
    //
    // LOGIN / AUTH
    //   Login (LinkedIn)           manual LinkedIn login, saves session to data/linkedin_auth.json
    //   Login Sites (Retry)        manual login for ATS sites that blocked apps, then resets those jobs
    //
    // REVIEW / MAINTENANCE
    //   Answer Questions           interactively fill unanswered form questions in answer bank
    //   Status                     show counts by job status
    //   List Jobs                  table of recent jobs (all statuses)
    //   View Applied               list successful applications + open folder
    //   View Failed                list failed applications + open folder
    //   Remove Failed              move failed app folders to _failed/ and clean DB
    //   Reset (Full Wipe)          delete all applications and database — fresh start
    // ============================================================
